-----------------------------------------
-	Simple Banking Application	-
-----------------------------------------

--------> run tests: python app_test.py
	
--------> available procedures:
	- show users in system
	- show transfers to user
	- register user in system
	- check user balance
	- create transfer request
	- handle incoming transfer request


-----------------------------------------
Create Database
-----------------------------------------
python db_create.py


-----------------------------------------
Database Schema Versioning
-----------------------------------------
---> check if database schema has changed:
python db_migrate.py

---> upgrade if changed:
python db_upgrade.py

---> downgrade if changed:
python db_downgrade.py

